## 📊 ATTENDANCE

### Mark Attendance (Teacher)

```javascript
// Mark single student
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('attendance')
  .insert({
    class_id: classId,
    student_id: studentId,
    status: 'present', // present, absent, late, excused
    marked_by: teacherProfileId
  });

// Mark multiple students
const attendanceRecords = students.map(student => ({
  class_id: classId,
  student_id: student.id,
  status: student.status,
  marked_by: teacherProfileId
}));

const { data } = await supabase
  .from('attendance')
  .upsert(attendanceRecords);
```

### Get Attendance Chart Data

```javascript
const { data } = await supabase.rpc('get_attendance_chart_data', {
  class_id_param: classId
});
// Returns: [{ date, present_count, absent_count, late_count, attendance_rate }]
```

### Get Student Attendance Rate

```javascript
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('attendance')
  .select('status')
  .eq('student_id', studentId)
  .then(result => {
    const total = result.data.length;
    const present = result.data.filter(a => a.status === 'present').length;
    return { rate: (present / total) * 100 };
  });
```

